<div class="w3-light-grey w3-large">
<div class="w3-container" id="about">
  <div class="w3-content" style="max-width:700px">
    <h5 class="w3-center"><span class="w3-tag w3-wide w3-padding-left w3-padding-right">About CareShare</span></h5>
    <p>CareShare is a community website allowing users to Connect, Share and Rate their experiences with healthcare, child care, senior care, special needs, & pet care providers in their area. </p>
    <p>CareShare ensures anonymity and provides a safe space for users to voice their concerns and suggestions regarding all caregiving professionals.</p>
    <p>Caregivers can feel safe in knowing that all reviews and ratings are subject to screeining in order to avoid profanity and keep unecessary negativity to a minimum.</p>
    <p>Please feel free to <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_path, class:"links" %> and share your caregiving experience!</p>
